ast.name: Herding Cats
ast.comment:
Herd cats onto flags. Tilt to herd; swipe to add fences; tap to shoo; you can even drag a cat onto a flag, but will it stay there? Have fun!

Tap the paws to add cats, up to 5 extra cats per level. More cats, more fun but is it easier?

Introduced a single screen version for Windows Phone Store. Original version can be recovered by setting the Single Screen variable to false in Main.

Added a Device Selection option to cope with differences between the phone app and the web app.

body.text: A page is pushed, forcing 'on page navigated from' to receive the phone back button.
Set this value to false to play the original game. Setting true gives the cut down single-screen game for the Windows Phone store first version.
